snippet.title: UNDERTALE PlayStation 4 Dynamic Theme "Ruins"
snippet.description:
It's UNDERTALE! Available now for PS4 and PS Vita!

Check out the dynamic "Ruins" theme, available for sale on the PS Store beginning September 15!
